		<body>
			<pb n="1R"/>
			<p rend="aligh(right)"><placeName>Claiborne</placeName> <date>May 14 5617</date>.</p>
				<p rend="align(center)"><addressee>Rev&#58; Isaac Leeser</addressee> <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>.</p>
				<p>Dear &#38; Respected sir&#33;</p>
				<p>I am sorely grieved for not being able<lb/> to comply with my promise&#44; in remitting the<lb/> subscriptions due you of last year&#44; as also the<lb/> <sic>Ballance</sic> on the <add>Hebrew</add>.  I have as yet not any money<lb/> collected&#44; <sic>allthough</sic> having hath the promise re&#758;<lb/>peatedly.  Gladly would I advance the whole<lb/> could I spare the amount.  But I am &#38; have<lb/> been for some time past greatly <sic>embarrast</sic>&#44;<lb/> so much so&#44; that I am unable to meet my own lia&#758;<lb/>bilities.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Believe me&#44; my dear sir&#44; that I feel exceedingly<lb/> mortified&#44; for not having <sic>remittet</sic> to <persName>Rev. Dr.<lb/> Lilienthal</persName> the Balance due him&#44; which places you<lb/> no doubt in <sic>a</sic> unpleasant situation&#44; more so&#44; as I am<lb/> an entire stranger to you&#44; nevertheless&#44; you hath the<lb/> kindness &#38; confidence in procuring the request ar&#758;<lb/><sic>tikles</sic>.  I have written to the Chief Rabbi praying for<lb/> indulgence until <add>Hebrew</add>.  By that time I shall by<lb/> all means raise the money&#44; &#38; <sic>endeaver</sic> to the utmost<lb/> to comply&#44; with this my promise.</p>
			<pb n="1V"/>
				<p>I shall also urge those&#44; who are in <sic>arrea.</sic> for the<lb/> subscription for the <sic>occident</sic>.</p>
				<p>With the sincere wish for your uninterrupted<lb/> welfare &#38; Happiness I remain</p>
				<p>Dear sir<lb/> your true &#38; sincere Friend</p>
				<p><add>Hebrew</add> <persName role="author">B M Emanuel</persName>.</p>
			<pb n="2V"/>
			<p rend="align(center)">Paid 10</p>
			<p rend="align(center)">Rev&#58; <hi rend="underline">Isaac</hi> <hi rend="underline"><addressee>Leeser</addressee></hi></p>
			<p rend="align(center)"><placeName><hi rend="underline">Philadelphia</hi></placeName></p>
		</body>
